title: An elegie on the Right Worshipful Sir Edmund-Bury Godfrey, Knight, one of His Majesties justices of the peace: who was found murtherd on Thursday the 17th of this instant October, 1678. in a ditch on the south-side of Primrose-Hill near Hampstead.
